<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "slawek1.jpeg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          <div class="skill">
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">
              <div
              class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
              role="progressbar"
              aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
              aria-valuemax="100"
              style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
              >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Aenean sit amet sagittis ex, sit amet dignissim diam. Cras euismod volutpat purus. Aenean sed scelerisque nibh, sed convallis nisi. Duis at venenatis ligula, eget tempor lorem. Proin lobortis felis orci, a tristique nunc pretium et. Curabitur dapibus nibh in suscipit semper. Phasellus a vehicula lorem, quis posuere nibh. Phasellus et egestas lacus. Mauris porttitor sem vel sem sollicitudin laoreet. Donec et libero mi.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job #1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job #2
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Education #1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Education #2
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>


      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
